divs: Sighting DetailsNothing to tell really, I was just going over photos when I noticed something different in the sky. When I zoomed in on the image it seemed to be very unusual, unidentified. The photo was taken at my son's special soccer game at the Naval Academy in Annapolis. I did not notice it when taking the photos. The original photo is attached and two that I had enhanced to define the image.
